{
  "chapter": 17,
  "title": "如果",
  "titleEn": "If",
  "topic": "假设、未来 / Hypotheticals, Conditionals",
  "grammar": [
    "如果...就",
    "要是...的话",
    "会"
  ],
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "对话一：图书馆——女生 (Library — Girls)",
      "en": "Dialogue 1: Library -- Girls."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "如果我跟王崩告白，你觉得他会说什么？",
      "en": "If I confessed to 王崩, what do you think he'd say?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "……你想听真话？",
      "en": "...you want the truth?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "真话。",
      "en": "The truth."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "他可能会说\"哦\"。",
      "en": "He'd probably say \"oh.\""
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "就\"哦\"？",
      "en": "Just \"oh\"?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "或者\"哦，谢谢\"。就是那种老师说\"很好，下一个\"的语气。",
      "en": "Or \"oh, thanks.\" Like when a teacher says \"good, next\" in that tone."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "……太惨了。",
      "en": "...that's brutal."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "但是club那晚以后……他坐在路边陪你。把外套给你了。",
      "en": "But after that night at the club... he sat on the curb with you. Gave you his jacket."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "那只是有礼貌。",
      "en": "That was just being polite."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "王崩从来不\"有礼貌\"。他对台湾有礼貌。对繁体字有礼貌。对人不太有礼貌。所以如果他把外套给你了……",
      "en": "王崩 is never \"polite.\" He's polite to Taiwan. Polite to traditional characters. Not very polite to people. So if he gave you his jacket..."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "……什么？",
      "en": "...what?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "也许是有意思的。",
      "en": "Maybe it means something."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "你觉得？",
      "en": "You think so?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "我觉得。如果你告诉他，最差的结果也就是一个\"哦谢谢\"。但至少你知道了。",
      "en": "I do. If you tell him, worst case is an \"oh thanks.\" But at least you'd know."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "如果他说\"哦谢谢\"我会死。",
      "en": "If he says \"oh thanks\" I will die."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "你不会死。",
      "en": "You won't die."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "精神上的。精神上会死。",
      "en": "Spiritually. I'll die spiritually."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "你呢？如果矮中约你，你会怎么说？",
      "en": "What about you? If 矮中 asked you out, what would you say?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "他不会约我。",
      "en": "He wouldn't ask me."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "假设。",
      "en": "Hypothetically."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "……",
      "en": "..."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "如果他请你吃饭呢？",
      "en": "What if he asked you to dinner?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "……如果他请我吃饭，我会说不。",
      "en": "...if he asked me to dinner, I'd say no."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "骗人。",
      "en": "Liar."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "我会说不。因为我知道他先约了小李，小李说无聊。我不要做别人的second choice。",
      "en": "I'd say no. Because I know he asked 小李 first, and 小李 said she was bored. I don't want to be someone's second choice."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "……这个思路很强。",
      "en": "...that's a strong take."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "我知道。",
      "en": "I know."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "xiaohei",
      "zh": "但也很sad。",
      "en": "But also pretty sad."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "qingqing",
      "zh": "……我也知道。",
      "en": "...I know that too."
    },
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "对话二：食堂——男生 (Cafeteria — Boys)",
      "en": "Dialogue 2: Cafeteria -- Boys."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "如果你可以跟班上的任何一个女生约会，你选谁？",
      "en": "If you could date any girl in our class, who would you pick?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "不选。",
      "en": "No one."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "不是这样玩\"如果\"的。假设。必须选。",
      "en": "That's not how you play \"if.\" Hypothetical. You have to pick."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "……",
      "en": "..."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "快说。",
      "en": "Come on, say it."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "……小黑不是最差的人。",
      "en": "...小黑 isn't the worst."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "哇。这是你说过的最浪漫的话。",
      "en": "Wow. That's the most romantic thing you've ever said."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "我说的是\"不是最差的\"。",
      "en": "I said \"not the worst.\""
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "对你来说这已经是情书了。",
      "en": "For you that's basically a love letter."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "闭嘴。",
      "en": "Shut up."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "你喜欢她什么？",
      "en": "What do you like about her?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "我没说我喜欢她。我说她不是最差的。",
      "en": "I didn't say I like her. I said she's not the worst."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "一样的。具体说。",
      "en": "Same thing. Be specific."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "她……跟我吵。但不是mean的那种。她其实在听我说台湾的事。她不同意，但她在听。别人都不听。",
      "en": "She... argues with me. But not in a mean way. She actually listens when I talk about Taiwan. She disagrees, but she listens. Nobody else listens."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "……所以你喜欢她因为她跟你吵？",
      "en": "...so you like her because she argues with you?"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "我喜欢她在乎到愿意吵。",
      "en": "I like that she cares enough to argue."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "这就是love language啊。",
      "en": "That's literally a love language."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "别说\"love language\"。",
      "en": "Don't say \"love language.\""
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "KMT遇上CCP！两岸romance！",
      "en": "KMT meets CCP! Cross-strait romance!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "我要走了。",
      "en": "I'm leaving."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "像毛泽东背叛蒋介石一样！但是romantic version！",
      "en": "Like Mao betraying Chiang Kai-shek! But the romantic version!"
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "那个一点都不romantic。几百万人死了。",
      "en": "That's not romantic at all. Millions of people died."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "……对。比喻不好。但你懂我的意思。",
      "en": "...right. Bad analogy. But you know what I mean."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "我不懂。",
      "en": "I don't."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "aizhong",
      "zh": "你的意思是你喜欢小黑。",
      "en": "What you mean is you like 小黑."
    },
    {
      "type": "line",
      "char": "wangbeng",
      "zh": "……吃你的饭。",
      "en": "...eat your food."
    },
    {
      "type": "scene",
      "text": "Ch 16: 是...的 (emphasizing details of past event)",
